<text><body>
<milestone n="1" unit="juan"/>
<pb n="0539a" ed="X" xml:id="X74.1479.0539a"/>
<lb n="0539a01" ed="X"/>
<lb n="0539a02" ed="X"/>
<lb n="0539a03" ed="X"/><cb:docNumber>No. 1479</cb:docNumber>
<lb n="0539a04" ed="X"/><lb n="0046a01" ed="R129"/><cb:juan n="1" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="1" type="卷"/><cb:jhead>孔雀尊經科儀</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb n="0539a05" ed="X"/><lb n="0046a02" ed="R129"/>
<lb n="0539a06" ed="X"/><lb n="0046a03" ed="R129"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu level="1" type="其他">前文</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pX74p0539a0601" style="margin-left:2em"><note place="inline">念大悲呪畢，洒淨。</note></p>
<lb n="0539a07" ed="X"/><lb n="0046a04" ed="R129"/><p xml:id="pX74p0539a0701">釋迦如來，如來說經教主。</p>
<lb n="0539a08" ed="X"/><lb n="0046a05" ed="R129"/><p xml:id="pX74p0539a0801">孔<g ref="#CB15179"/>如來，如來降臨法會。</p>
<lb n="0539a09" ed="X"/><lb n="0046a06" ed="R129"/><p xml:id="pX74p0539a0901">阿難陀！尊者、尊者同垂加護。</p>
<lb n="0539a10" ed="X"/><lb n="0046a07" ed="R129"/><p xml:id="pX74p0539a1001">切以旃檀林內，六銖價重於娑婆。給孤園中，一炷通
<lb n="0539a11" ed="X"/><lb n="0046a08" ed="R129"/>津於靈鷲。古<g ref="#CB16967"/>盤旋清瑞氣，玉爐繚遶碧祥雲。我今
<lb n="0539a12" ed="X"/><lb n="0046a09" ed="R129"/>熱處獻如來，唯願慈悲哀納受。仰啟。</p>
<lb n="0539a13" ed="X"/><lb n="0046a10" ed="R129"/><p xml:id="pX74p0539a1301">聖中聖主，天中天王。世出世間，名稱普聞。拔循環救
<lb n="0539a14" ed="X"/><lb n="0046a11" ed="R129"/>苦之慈父，濟業海利樂之導師。應願似空谷傳聲，赴
<lb n="0539a15" ed="X"/><lb n="0046a12" ed="R129"/>感若春回大聲。五天調御，三界世雄。降臨道場，作乎
<lb n="0539a16" ed="X"/><lb n="0046a13" ed="R129"/>明證。<note place="inline">通情念</note></p>
<lb n="0539a17" ed="X"/><lb n="0046a14" ed="R129"/><lg xml:id="lgX74p0539a1701" type="regular"><l>本師釋迦牟尼佛，<caesura></caesura>孔<g ref="#CB15179"/>海會佛菩薩，</l>
<lb n="0539a18" ed="X"/><lb n="0046a15" ed="R129"/><l>䒶龍八部降吉祥，<caesura></caesura>摩訶般若波羅蜜。</l></lg>
<lb n="0539a19" ed="X"/><lb n="0046a16" ed="R129"/><p xml:id="pX74p0539a1901">蓋聞孔<g ref="#CB15179"/>明王經者，經名孔<g ref="#CB15179"/>，說佛姥之因緣。呪說
<lb n="0539a20" ed="X"/><lb n="0046a17" ed="R129"/>毒蛇，救眾生之患難。所求所請，隨願隨心。飲食鋪排，
<lb n="0539a21" ed="X"/><lb n="0046a18" ed="R129"/><note n="0539001" resp="Xuzangjing" type="orig" place="foot text">各字疑剩</note>各香花供養。各生歡喜，咸听加持。真言演處，四百四
<lb n="0539a22" ed="X"/><lb n="0046b01" ed="R129"/>病盡消除。密語宣時，萬禍萬殃俱殄滅。天神、地神、水
<lb n="0539a23" ed="X"/><lb n="0046b02" ed="R129"/>神、藥叉神，稽首歸依。山王、龍王、河王、大仙，傾心敬仰。
<lb n="0539a24" ed="X"/><lb n="0046b03" ed="R129"/>羅<note n="0539002" resp="Xuzangjing" type="orig" place="foot text">又疑剎</note>又女不能為害，藥叉將總願垂祥。灾星變作福星，
<pb n="0539b" ed="X" xml:id="X74.1479.0539b"/>
<lb n="0539b01" ed="X"/><lb n="0046b04" ed="R129"/>惡曜化為吉曜。公私口舌似氷消，厭魅蠱毒而霧散。
<lb n="0539b02" ed="X"/><lb n="0046b05" ed="R129"/>在官者清平吉利，居家者福壽康寧。若老若少保安
<lb n="0539b03" ed="X"/><lb n="0046b06" ed="R129"/>康，是男是女皆<note n="0539003" resp="Xuzangjing" type="orig" place="foot text">慶上疑脫欣字</note>慶。明王威力，週遍河沙。嘆莫能窮，讚
<lb n="0539b04" ed="X"/><lb n="0046b07" ed="R129"/>揚難盡。欲開大部靈文，先稱七佛嘉號。尊眾毋勞，隨
<lb n="0539b05" ed="X"/><lb n="0046b08" ed="R129"/>言後和。</p>
<lb n="0539b06" ed="X"/><lb n="0046b09" ed="R129"/><list rend="no-marker"><item xml:id="itemX74p0539b0601">孔<g ref="#CB15179"/>明王佛</item><item xml:id="itemX74p0539b0606">大孔<g ref="#CB15179"/>明王佛</item>
<lb n="0539b07" ed="X"/><lb n="0046b10" ed="R129"/><item xml:id="itemX74p0539b0701">金耀孔<g ref="#CB15179"/>明王佛</item><item xml:id="itemX74p0539b0708">佛姥大孔<g ref="#CB15179"/>明王佛</item>
<lb n="0539b08" ed="X"/><lb n="0046b11" ed="R129"/><item xml:id="itemX74p0539b0801">明王佛明王佛</item>
<lb n="0539b09" ed="X"/><lb n="0046b12" ed="R129"/><item xml:id="itemX74p0539b0901">雪山南面金耀佛姥大孔<g ref="#CB15179"/>明王佛</item></list>
<lb n="0539b10" ed="X"/><lb n="0046b13" ed="R129"/><p xml:id="pX74p0539b1001">出靈鷲山，人天敬仰。遊鹿野苑，轉大法輪。仰讚洪慈，
<lb n="0539b11" ed="X"/><lb n="0046b14" ed="R129"/>俯垂明證。茲辰誦經開啟，有意敷陳。大圓鏡中，諒垂
<lb n="0539b12" ed="X"/><lb n="0046b15" ed="R129"/>昭鑒。茲據<note place="inline">入意</note>。</p>
<lb n="0539b13" ed="X"/><lb n="0046b16" ed="R129"/><p xml:id="pX74p0539b1301">即日沐手然香，拜于
<lb n="0539b14" ed="X" type="honorific"/><lb n="0046b17" ed="R129"/>雪山教主孔<g ref="#CB15179"/>能仁，願展金眸，鑒茲微懇。吉於　年
<lb n="0539b15" ed="X"/><lb n="0046b18" ed="R129"/>　月　日，請命僧眾，于家供佛作證，演念佛姆大孔
<lb n="0539b16" ed="X"/><lb n="0047a01" ed="R129"/><g ref="#CB15179"/>明王尊經，加持經文神呪，稱揚萬德洪名。所集功
<lb n="0539b17" ed="X"/><lb n="0047a02" ed="R129"/>德，先伸回向
<lb n="0539b18" ed="X" type="honorific"/><lb n="0047a03" ed="R129"/>廣大真如實際，莊嚴無<note n="0539004" resp="Xuzangjing" type="orig" place="foot text">工疑上次同</note>工佛果菩提。<note type="star" corresp="#0539004"></note>工酧佛祖之深
<lb n="0539b19" ed="X"/><lb n="0047a04" ed="R129"/>恩，次答龍天之厚德。祝扶
<lb n="0539b20" ed="X" type="honorific"/><lb n="0047a05" ed="R129"/>當生本命星官，照臨吉威乾像。惟願等一真慈，同納
<lb n="0539b21" ed="X"/><lb n="0047a06" ed="R129"/>功德，共降禎祥。所冀　向去身安壽求，福集灾消，在
<lb n="0539b22" ed="X"/><lb n="0047a07" ed="R129"/>佛光中，吉祥如意。上來開啟，情悃如斯，仰勞尊眾，不
<lb n="0539b23" ed="X"/><lb n="0047a08" ed="R129"/>倦慈悲，振鈴讀誦。佛姆大孔<g ref="#CB15179"/>明王經前啟請法
<lb n="0539b24" ed="X"/><lb n="0047a09" ed="R129"/><note place="inline">入經畢</note>。</p>
<pb n="0539c" ed="X" xml:id="X74.1479.0539c"/>
<lb n="0539c01" ed="X"/><lb n="0047a10" ed="R129"/><p xml:id="pX74p0539c0101">舉如意輪王菩薩摩訶薩。</p>
<lb n="0539c02" ed="X"/><lb n="0047a11" ed="R129"/><p xml:id="pX74p0539c0201" cb:type="dharani">至滿怛囉莎縛賀<note place="inline">舉一切天神咸集會</note></p>
<lb n="0539c03" ed="X"/><lb n="0047a12" ed="R129"/><p xml:id="pX74p0539c0301">因緣自性所出生，所有種種微妙花，香燈塗果供養，
<lb n="0539c04" ed="X"/><lb n="0047a13" ed="R129"/>奉獻上師三寶尊，惟願慈悲哀納受。</p>
<lb n="0539c05" ed="X"/><lb n="0047a14" ed="R129"/><p xml:id="pX74p0539c0501" cb:type="dharani">戶唵薩哩縛怛佗誐哆唵布瑟畢度畢阿盧計頞底
<lb n="0539c06" ed="X"/><lb n="0047a15" ed="R129"/>儞尾底捨不達布㘃𡄣迦三摩怛囉薩普囉曩三摩
<lb n="0539c07" ed="X"/><lb n="0047a16" ed="R129"/>耶吽</p>
<lb n="0539c08" ed="X"/><lb n="0047a17" ed="R129"/><p xml:id="pX74p0539c0801" style="margin-left:1em">奉香華自在明王佛。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0539c09" ed="X"/><lb n="0047a18" ed="R129"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu level="1" type="其他">結界　持國天王降吉祥</cb:mulu><head>結界　持國天王降吉祥</head>
<lb n="0539c10" ed="X"/><lb n="0047b01" ed="R129"/><lg xml:id="lgX74p0539c1001" type="regular"><l>東方世界主，<caesura></caesura>持國大天王，</l>
<lb n="0539c11" ed="X"/><lb n="0047b02" ed="R129"/><l>統領彥達嚩，<caesura></caesura>結成瑜伽界。</l>
<lb n="0539c12" ed="X"/><lb n="0047b03" ed="R129"/><l>南方世界主，<caesura></caesura>增長大天王，</l>
<lb n="0539c13" ed="X"/><lb n="0047b04" ed="R129"/><l>統領矩畔拏，<caesura></caesura>結成灌頂界。</l>
<lb n="0539c14" ed="X"/><lb n="0047b05" ed="R129"/><l>西方世界主，<caesura></caesura>廣目大天王，</l>
<lb n="0539c15" ed="X"/><lb n="0047b06" ed="R129"/><l>統領大龍主，<caesura></caesura>結成蓮華界。</l>
<lb n="0539c16" ed="X"/><lb n="0047b07" ed="R129"/><l>北方世界主，<caesura></caesura>多聞大天王，</l>
<lb n="0539c17" ed="X"/><lb n="0047b08" ed="R129"/><l>統領藥叉主，<caesura></caesura>結成羯磨界。</l>
<lb n="0539c18" ed="X"/><lb n="0047b09" ed="R129"/><l>中方世界主，<caesura></caesura>大梵大天王，</l>
<lb n="0539c19" ed="X"/><lb n="0047b10" ed="R129"/><l>統領人天眾，<caesura></caesura>結成瑜伽界。</l></lg>
<lb n="0539c20" ed="X"/><lb n="0047b11" ed="R129"/><lg xml:id="lgX74p0539c2001" type="regular"><l>東方世界主，<caesura></caesura>佛號阿閦尊，<caesura></caesura>流演妙伽陀，</l>
<lb n="0539c21" ed="X"/><lb n="0047b12" ed="R129"/><l>結成金剛界。</l></lg>
<lb n="0539c22" ed="X"/><lb n="0047b13" ed="R129"/><lg xml:id="lgX74p0539c2201" type="regular"><l>南方世界主，<caesura></caesura>佛號寶生尊，<caesura></caesura>流演妙伽陀，</l>
<lb n="0539c23" ed="X"/><lb n="0047b14" ed="R129"/><l>結成蓮華界。</l></lg>
<lb n="0539c24" ed="X"/><lb n="0047b15" ed="R129"/><lg xml:id="lgX74p0539c2401" type="regular"><l>北方世界主，<caesura></caesura>佛號成就尊，<caesura></caesura>流演妙伽陀，</l>
<pb n="0540a" ed="X" xml:id="X74.1479.0540a"/>
<lb n="0540a01" ed="X"/><lb n="0047b16" ed="R129"/><l>結成羯磨界。</l></lg>
<lb n="0540a02" ed="X"/><lb n="0047b17" ed="R129"/><lg xml:id="lgX74p0540a0201" type="regular"><l>中方世界主，<caesura></caesura>佛號毗盧尊，<caesura></caesura>流演妙伽陀，</l>
<lb n="0540a03" ed="X"/><lb n="0047b18" ed="R129"/><l>結成瑜伽界。</l></lg>
<lb n="0540a04" ed="X"/><lb n="0048a01" ed="R129"/><lg xml:id="lgX74p0540a0401" type="regular"><l>奉請東方阿閦佛，<caesura></caesura>其身青色放光明，</l>
<lb n="0540a05" ed="X"/><lb n="0048a02" ed="R129"/><l>手印執持降魔杵，<caesura></caesura>眾等志心歸命禮。</l>
<lb n="0540a06" ed="X"/><lb n="0048a03" ed="R129"/><l>今將密語遶香壇，<caesura></caesura>憑此結成金剛界。</l>
<lb n="0540a07" ed="X"/><lb n="0048a04" ed="R129"/><l>奉請南方寶生佛，<caesura></caesura>其身赤色放光明，</l>
<lb n="0540a08" ed="X"/><lb n="0048a05" ed="R129"/><l>手印執持摩尼寶，<caesura></caesura>眾等志心歸命禮。</l>
<lb n="0540a09" ed="X"/><lb n="0048a06" ed="R129"/><l>今將密語遶香壇，<caesura></caesura>憑此結成灌頂界。</l>
<lb n="0540a10" ed="X"/><lb n="0048a07" ed="R129"/><l>奉請西方彌陀佛，<caesura></caesura>其身白色放光明，</l>
<lb n="0540a11" ed="X"/><lb n="0048a08" ed="R129"/><l>手印執持妙蓮花，<caesura></caesura>眾等志心歸命禮。</l>
<lb n="0540a12" ed="X"/><lb n="0048a09" ed="R129"/><l>今將密語遶香壇，<caesura></caesura>憑此結成蓮華界。</l>
<lb n="0540a13" ed="X"/><lb n="0048a10" ed="R129"/><l>奉請北方成就佛，<caesura></caesura>其身黑色放光明，</l>
<lb n="0540a14" ed="X"/><lb n="0048a11" ed="R129"/><l>手印執持妙降魔，<caesura></caesura>眾等志心歸命禮。</l>
<lb n="0540a15" ed="X"/><lb n="0048a12" ed="R129"/><l>今將密語遶香壇，<caesura></caesura>憑此結成羯磨界。</l>
<lb n="0540a16" ed="X"/><lb n="0048a13" ed="R129"/><l>奉請中方毗盧佛，<caesura></caesura>其身黃色放光明，</l>
<lb n="0540a17" ed="X"/><lb n="0048a14" ed="R129"/><l>手印執持千輻輪，<caesura></caesura>眾等志心歸命禮。</l>
<lb n="0540a18" ed="X"/><lb n="0048a15" ed="R129"/><l>今將密語遶香壇，<caesura></caesura>憑此結成瑜伽界。</l></lg>
<lb n="0540a19" ed="X"/><lb n="0048a16" ed="R129"/><p xml:id="pX74p0540a1901">集福迎祥，幢幡為寶蓋，振動金鈴，殄滅諸。</p>
<lb n="0540a20" ed="X"/><lb n="0048a17" ed="R129"/><list rend="no-marker"><item xml:id="itemX74p0540a2001">阿閦</item><item xml:id="itemX74p0540a2003">持國</item>
<lb n="0540a21" ed="X"/><lb n="0048a18" ed="R129"/><item xml:id="itemX74p0540a2101">寶生</item><item xml:id="itemX74p0540a2103">增長</item></list>
<lb n="0540a22" ed="X"/><lb n="0048b01" ed="R129"/><p xml:id="pX74p0540a2201">妖恠彌陀佛。如來慈悲甚廣大，廣目天王來。</p>
<lb n="0540a23" ed="X"/><lb n="0048b02" ed="R129"/><list rend="no-marker"><item xml:id="itemX74p0540a2301">成就</item><item xml:id="itemX74p0540a2303">多聞</item>
<lb n="0540a24" ed="X"/><lb n="0048b03" ed="R129"/><item xml:id="itemX74p0540a2401">毗盧</item><item xml:id="itemX74p0540a2403">大梵</item></list>
<pb n="0540b" ed="X" xml:id="X74.1479.0540b"/>
<lb n="0540b01" ed="X"/><lb n="0048b04" ed="R129"/>
<lb n="0540b02" ed="X"/><lb n="0048b05" ed="R129"/><p xml:id="pX74p0540b0201">結蓮華界　金剛　灌頂　羯磨　瑜伽。</p>
<lb n="0540b03" ed="X"/><lb n="0048b06" ed="R129"/><lg xml:id="lgX74p0540b0301"><l>天、阿蘇來、藥叉等<note place="inline">摩訶摩瑜利金耀界云云</note>，</l>
<lb n="0540b04" ed="X"/><lb n="0048b07" ed="R129"/><l>來听法者應志心<note place="inline">南無大摩訶摩瑜利</note>。</l></lg>
<lb n="0540b05" ed="X"/><lb n="0048b08" ed="R129"/><p xml:id="pX74p0540b0501">孔<g ref="#CB15179"/>明王佛<note place="inline">云云</note>。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0540b06" ed="X"/><lb n="0048b09" ed="R129"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu level="1" type="其他">上卷圓滿保平安</cb:mulu><head>上卷圓滿保平安</head>
<lb n="0540b07" ed="X"/><lb n="0048b10" ed="R129"/><p xml:id="pX74p0540b0701">南無大孔<g ref="#CB15179"/>明王佛。　歸命禮真如沒䭾耶。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0540b08" ed="X"/><lb n="0048b11" ed="R129"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu level="1" type="其他">中卷藥叉</cb:mulu><head>中卷藥叉</head>
<lb n="0540b09" ed="X"/><lb n="0048b12" ed="R129"/><p xml:id="pX74p0540b0901">奉藥叉聖眾降吉祥。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0540b10" ed="X"/><lb n="0048b13" ed="R129"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu level="1" type="其他">掛金索</cb:mulu><head>掛金索</head>
<lb n="0540b11" ed="X"/><lb n="0048b14" ed="R129"/><p xml:id="pX74p0540b1101">戒定真香，焚氣衝天上。施主虔誠，爇在金爐放。頃刻
<lb n="0540b12" ed="X"/><lb n="0048b15" ed="R129"/>氛氤，即遍滿十方。昔日耶輸，免難除灾障。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0540b13" ed="X"/><lb n="0048b16" ed="R129"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu level="1" type="其他">寄生草</cb:mulu><head>寄生草</head>
<lb n="0540b14" ed="X"/><lb n="0048b17" ed="R129"/><p xml:id="pX74p0540b1401">香，纔爇爐焚寶<g ref="#CB16967"/>中。旃檀<note n="0540001" resp="Xuzangjing" type="orig" place="foot text">況疑沈</note>況乳真堪供，祥雲繚遶蓮
<lb n="0540b15" ed="X"/><lb n="0048b18" ed="R129"/>華動。十方諸佛下天宮，清涼山羅漢來受人間供。
<lb n="0540b16" ed="X" type="honorific"/><lb n="0049a01" ed="R129"/>明王佛。揭句寸那神藥叉將。波吒黎手處藥叉神。䟦
<lb n="0540b17" ed="X"/><lb n="0049a02" ed="R129"/>阿囉<g ref="#CB14031"/>哆藥叉王，住窣吐奴邑。賢善大藥叉，住於世
<lb n="0540b18" ed="X"/><lb n="0049a03" ed="R129"/>囉城。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0540b19" ed="X"/><lb n="0049a04" ed="R129"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu level="1" type="其他">清江引</cb:mulu><head>清江引</head>
<lb n="0540b20" ed="X"/><lb n="0049a05" ed="R129"/><p xml:id="pX74p0540b2001">牛首旃檀香供養，裊裊祥雲起。透上九霄中，結成香
<lb n="0540b21" ed="X"/><lb n="0049a06" ed="R129"/>雲蓋。唯願慈悲哀納受。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0540b22" ed="X"/><lb n="0049a07" ed="R129"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu level="1" type="其他">浪淘沙</cb:mulu><head>浪淘沙</head>
<lb n="0540b23" ed="X"/><lb n="0049a08" ed="R129"/><p xml:id="pX74p0540b2301">沉乳共旃檀。馥郁馨香。金爐纔熱遍十方。昔日耶輸
<lb n="0540b24" ed="X"/><lb n="0049a09" ed="R129"/>曾免難，火內除殃。</p></cb:div>
<pb n="0540c" ed="X" xml:id="X74.1479.0540c"/>
<lb n="0540c01" ed="X"/><lb n="0049a10" ed="R129"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu level="1" type="其他">七懺悔　求哀懺悔明王佛</cb:mulu><head>七懺悔　求哀懺悔明王佛</head>
<lb n="0540c02" ed="X"/><lb n="0049a11" ed="R129"/><lg xml:id="lgX74p0540c0201" type="regular"><l>三千界內慈悲主，<caesura></caesura>百億洲中大法王，</l>
<lb n="0540c03" ed="X"/><lb n="0049a12" ed="R129"/><l>咸開慧目鑒凡情，<caesura></caesura>眾生有求皆感應。</l></lg>
<lb n="0540c04" ed="X"/><lb n="0049a13" ed="R129"/><p xml:id="pX74p0540c0401" style="margin-left:1em"><note place="inline">讚嘆三寶，恭請證明。我為今辰演經信□泊家眷等，目茲演經<note n="0540002" resp="Xuzangjing" type="orig" place="foot text">問疑向</note>〔問〕去各人身中所有病苦云云，願早安痊</note>。
<lb n="0540c05" ed="X"/><lb n="0049a14" ed="R129"/>能離病苦明王佛。</p>
<lb n="0540c06" ed="X"/><lb n="0049a15" ed="R129"/><lg xml:id="lgX74p0540c0601" type="regular"><l>佛住真如法界內，<caesura></caesura>無相無形離諸垢，</l>
<lb n="0540c07" ed="X"/><lb n="0049a16" ed="R129"/><l>眾生觀見種種身，<caesura></caesura>一切恐怖皆遠離。</l></lg>
<lb n="0540c08" ed="X"/><lb n="0049a17" ed="R129"/><p xml:id="pX74p0540c0801" style="margin-left:1em">能除恐怖，　恐怖恐怖，悉皆遠離。</p>
<lb n="0540c09" ed="X"/><lb n="0049a18" ed="R129"/><lg xml:id="lgX74p0540c0901" type="regular"><l>解結解結解冤結，<caesura></caesura>解了多生冤和業。</l>
<lb n="0540c10" ed="X"/><lb n="0049b01" ed="R129"/><l>冤家債<note n="0540003" resp="Xuzangjing" type="orig" place="foot text">生疑主</note>生兩相逢，<caesura></caesura>相逢相遇相歡悅。</l></lg>
<lb n="0540c11" ed="X"/><lb n="0049b02" ed="R129"/><p xml:id="pX74p0540c1101" style="margin-left:1em">冤家冤家，各相歡喜，　解冤釋結。</p>
<lb n="0540c12" ed="X"/><lb n="0049b03" ed="R129"/><lg xml:id="lgX74p0540c1201" type="regular"><l>明王經力不思議，<caesura></caesura>救度眾生無盡期。</l>
<lb n="0540c13" ed="X"/><lb n="0049b04" ed="R129"/><l>施主志心歸命禮，<caesura></caesura>不饒益事皆饒益。</l></lg>
<lb n="0540c14" ed="X"/><lb n="0049b05" ed="R129"/><p xml:id="pX74p0540c1401" style="margin-left:1em">不饒益事，廣大饒益，　廣大饒益，</p>
<lb n="0540c15" ed="X"/><lb n="0049b06" ed="R129"/><lg xml:id="lgX74p0540c1501" type="regular"><l>四八端嚴微妙相，<caesura></caesura>僧祇三大刧修來。</l>
<lb n="0540c16" ed="X"/><lb n="0049b07" ed="R129"/><l>面如滿月目如蓮，<caesura></caesura>天上人間咸恭敬。</l></lg>
<lb n="0540c17" ed="X"/><lb n="0049b08" ed="R129"/><p xml:id="pX74p0540c1701" style="margin-left:1em">毒藥毒藥，化為甘露，　化為甘露，</p>
<lb n="0540c18" ed="X"/><lb n="0049b09" ed="R129"/><lg xml:id="lgX74p0540c1801" type="regular"><l>䒶上天下無如佛，<caesura></caesura>十方世界亦無比，</l>
<lb n="0540c19" ed="X"/><lb n="0049b10" ed="R129"/><l>世間所有我盡見，<caesura></caesura>一切無有如佛者。</l></lg>
<lb n="0540c20" ed="X"/><lb n="0049b11" ed="R129"/><p xml:id="pX74p0540c2001" style="margin-left:1em">佗人厭禱，悉皆消滅。　能離厭禱，</p>
<lb n="0540c21" ed="X"/><lb n="0049b12" ed="R129"/><lg xml:id="lgX74p0540c2101" type="regular"><l>一障二語三毒罪，<caesura></caesura>四重五逆六根𠎝。</l>
<lb n="0540c22" ed="X"/><lb n="0049b13" ed="R129"/><l>七遮八難罪消容，<caesura></caesura>九結十纏皆懺悔。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb n="0540c23" ed="X"/><lb n="0049b14" ed="R129"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu level="1" type="其他">懺除罪業　五言偈</cb:mulu><head>懺除罪業　五言偈</head>
<lb n="0540c24" ed="X"/><lb n="0049b15" ed="R129"/><lg xml:id="lgX74p0540c2401" type="regular"><l>頂中紅肉髻。<caesura></caesura>如日映青山。<caesura></caesura>眉間白玉毫。</l>
<pb n="0541a" ed="X" xml:id="X74.1479.0541a"/>
<lb n="0541a01" ed="X"/><lb n="0049b16" ed="R129"/><l>似月臨滄海。</l></lg>
<lb n="0541a02" ed="X"/><lb n="0049b17" ed="R129"/><lg xml:id="lgX74p0541a0201" type="regular"><l>稽首天中天。<caesura></caesura>降誕毗藍園。<caesura></caesura>分手指天地。</l>
<lb n="0541a03" ed="X"/><lb n="0049b18" ed="R129"/><l>七步躡紅蓮。</l></lg>
<lb n="0541a04" ed="X"/><lb n="0050a01" ed="R129"/><lg xml:id="lgX74p0541a0401" type="regular"><l>海印澄三昧，<caesura></caesura>慈光照十方。<caesura></caesura>弘施十二願，</l>
<lb n="0541a05" ed="X"/><lb n="0050a02" ed="R129"/><l>故號法中王。</l></lg>
<lb n="0541a06" ed="X"/><lb n="0050a03" ed="R129"/><lg xml:id="lgX74p0541a0601" type="regular"><l>菩<note n="0541001" resp="Xuzangjing" type="orig" place="foot text">薩疑提</note>薩清涼月，<caesura></caesura>猶如碧鏡空，<caesura></caesura>眾生心水淨，</l>
<lb n="0541a07" ed="X"/><lb n="0050a04" ed="R129"/><l>菩薩影現中。</l></lg>
<lb n="0541a08" ed="X"/><lb n="0050a05" ed="R129"/><lg xml:id="lgX74p0541a0801" type="regular"><l>百刧千生罪。<caesura></caesura>一念蕩消除，<caesura></caesura>似<note n="0541002" resp="Xuzangjing" type="orig" place="foot text">大疑火</note>大焚枯草。</l>
<lb n="0541a09" ed="X"/><lb n="0050a06" ed="R129"/><l>滅盡無有餘。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb n="0541a10" ed="X"/><lb n="0050a07" ed="R129"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu level="1" type="其他">四言</cb:mulu><head>四言</head>
<lb n="0541a11" ed="X"/><lb n="0050a08" ed="R129"/><lg xml:id="lgX74p0541a1101" type="regular"><l>佛真法身，<caesura></caesura>猶若虗空，<caesura></caesura>應物現形，</l>
<lb n="0541a12" ed="X"/><lb n="0050a09" ed="R129"/><l>如水月中。</l></lg>
<lb n="0541a13" ed="X"/><lb n="0050a10" ed="R129"/><lg xml:id="lgX74p0541a1301" type="regular"><l>大圓滿覺，<caesura></caesura>應跡西乾，<caesura></caesura>心包太虗。</l>
<lb n="0541a14" ed="X"/><lb n="0050a11" ed="R129"/><l>量週沙界。</l></lg>
<lb n="0541a15" ed="X"/><lb n="0050a12" ed="R129"/><lg xml:id="lgX74p0541a1501" type="regular"><l>佛法僧寶，<caesura></caesura>眾生福田，<caesura></caesura>凡在禱祈，</l>
<lb n="0541a16" ed="X"/><lb n="0050a13" ed="R129"/><l>必彰感應。</l></lg>
<lb n="0541a17" ed="X"/><lb n="0050a14" ed="R129"/><lg xml:id="lgX74p0541a1701" type="regular"><l>常住三寶，<caesura></caesura>體徧十方，<caesura></caesura>隨眾生心，</l>
<lb n="0541a18" ed="X"/><lb n="0050a15" ed="R129"/><l>感而應現。</l></lg>
<lb n="0541a19" ed="X"/><lb n="0050a16" ed="R129"/><lg xml:id="lgX74p0541a1901" type="regular"><l>佛功德山，<caesura></caesura>惟高惟聳；<caesura></caesura>法智慧海，</l>
<lb n="0541a20" ed="X"/><lb n="0050a17" ed="R129"/><l>最廣最深。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb n="0541a21" ed="X"/><lb n="0050a18" ed="R129"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu level="1" type="其他">羅剎女　羅剎女眾降吉祥</cb:mulu><head>羅剎女　羅剎女眾降吉祥</head>
<lb n="0541a22" ed="X"/><lb n="0050b01" ed="R129"/><list rend="no-marker"><item xml:id="itemX74p0541a2201">羅剎女眾降吉祥</item><item xml:id="itemX74p0541a2208">羅剎女眾降大吉祥</item>
<lb n="0541a23" ed="X"/><lb n="0050b02" ed="R129"/><item xml:id="itemX74p0541a2301">羅剎女眾降吉祥</item><item xml:id="itemX74p0541a2308">消灾障</item>
<lb n="0541a24" ed="X"/><lb n="0050b03" ed="R129"/><item xml:id="itemX74p0541a2401">羅利女眾降大吉祥</item></list></cb:div>
<pb n="0541b" ed="X" xml:id="X74.1479.0541b"/>
<lb n="0541b01" ed="X"/><lb n="0050b04" ed="R129"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu level="1" type="其他">四平聲　龍王聖眾降吉祥</cb:mulu><head>四平聲　龍王聖眾降吉祥</head>
<lb n="0541b02" ed="X"/><lb n="0050b05" ed="R129"/><list rend="no-marker"><item xml:id="itemX74p0541b0201">佛世尊龍王龍樹王</item><item xml:id="itemX74p0541b0209">梵天龍王大龍王</item>
<lb n="0541b03" ed="X"/><lb n="0050b06" ed="R129"/><item xml:id="itemX74p0541b0301">帝釋龍王消障灾</item><item xml:id="itemX74p0541b0308">𦦨摩龍王保安康</item></list></cb:div>
<lb n="0541b04" ed="X"/><lb n="0050b07" ed="R129"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu level="1" type="其他">蜜峯採華</cb:mulu><head>蜜<note n="0541003" resp="Xuzangjing" type="orig" place="foot text">峯疑蜂</note>峯採華</head>
<lb n="0541b05" ed="X"/><lb n="0050b08" ed="R129"/><list rend="no-marker"><item xml:id="itemX74p0541b0501">佛世尊龍王梵天龍王龍樹王菩薩</item>
<lb n="0541b06" ed="X"/><lb n="0050b09" ed="R129"/><item xml:id="itemX74p0541b0601">𦦨摩龍王大海龍王南無龍樹王菩薩</item></list></cb:div>
<lb n="0541b07" ed="X"/><lb n="0050b10" ed="R129"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu level="1" type="其他">清江引</cb:mulu><head>清江引</head>
<lb n="0541b08" ed="X"/><lb n="0050b11" ed="R129"/><list rend="no-marker"><item xml:id="itemX74p0541b0801">天阿蘇來藥叉等</item><item xml:id="itemX74p0541b0808">來听法者應志心</item>
<lb n="0541b09" ed="X"/><lb n="0050b12" ed="R129"/><item xml:id="itemX74p0541b0901">孔<g ref="#CB15179"/>明王經</item><item xml:id="itemX74p0541b0906">請佛作證明</item></list>
<lb n="0541b10" ed="X"/><lb n="0050b13" ed="R129"/><lg xml:id="lgX74p0541b1001" type="regular"><l>大慈大悲，<caesura></caesura>救苦救難。<caesura></caesura>千手千眼，</l>
<lb n="0541b11" ed="X"/><lb n="0050b14" ed="R129"/><l>水月光中，<caesura></caesura>普陀岩畔，<caesura></caesura>一葉扁舟。</l>
<lb n="0541b12" ed="X"/><lb n="0050b15" ed="R129"/><l>白衣妙相，<caesura></caesura>紫竹林中，<caesura></caesura>風波浪內。</l>
<lb n="0541b13" ed="X"/><lb n="0050b16" ed="R129"/><l>隨心滿願。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb n="0541b14" ed="X"/><lb n="0050b17" ed="R129"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu level="1" type="其他">金字經</cb:mulu><head>金字經</head>
<lb n="0541b15" ed="X"/><lb n="0050b18" ed="R129"/><list rend="no-marker"><item xml:id="itemX74p0541b1501">天阿蘇囉藥叉等</item><item xml:id="itemX74p0541b1508">來听法者應志心</item>
<lb n="0541b16" ed="X"/><lb n="0051a01" ed="R129"/><item xml:id="itemX74p0541b1601">孔<g ref="#CB15179"/>明王經</item><item xml:id="itemX74p0541b1606">大慈大悲觀世音</item></list>
<lb n="0541b17" ed="X"/><lb n="0051a02" ed="R129"/><p xml:id="pX74p0541b1701">消灾障。唵嚤呢叭𠺗吽。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0541b18" ed="X"/><lb n="0051a03" ed="R129"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu level="1" type="其他">採茶聲</cb:mulu><head>採茶聲</head>
<lb n="0541b19" ed="X"/><lb n="0051a04" ed="R129"/><lg xml:id="lgX74p0541b1901" type="regular"><l>天阿蘇囉藥叉等，<caesura></caesura>來听法者應志心，</l>
<lb n="0541b20" ed="X"/><lb n="0051a05" ed="R129"/><l>孔<g ref="#CB15179"/>明王明王佛，<caesura></caesura>消灾延壽保平安。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb n="0541b21" ed="X"/><lb n="0051a06" ed="R129"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu level="1" type="其他">中卷圓滿保平安</cb:mulu><head>中卷圓滿保平安<note place="inline">同前</note></head></cb:div>
<lb n="0541b22" ed="X"/><lb n="0051a07" ed="R129"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu level="1" type="其他">至七佛　微鉢尸如來降吉祥</cb:mulu><head>至七佛　微鉢尸如來降吉祥</head>
<lb n="0541b23" ed="X"/><lb n="0051a08" ed="R129"/><lg xml:id="lgX74p0541b2301" type="regular"><l>巍巍大法王，<caesura></caesura>毫光照大千，<caesura></caesura>八風吹不動。</l>
<lb n="0541b24" ed="X"/><lb n="0051a09" ed="R129"/><l>一朵紫金蓮，<caesura></caesura>尸棄如來<note place="inline">同前</note>。</l></lg>
<pb n="0541c" ed="X" xml:id="X74.1479.0541c"/>
<lb n="0541c01" ed="X"/><lb n="0051a10" ed="R129"/><lg xml:id="lgX74p0541c0101" type="regular"><l>相好真金色。<caesura></caesura>無邊淨法身。<caesura></caesura>素容登寶座。</l>
<lb n="0541c02" ed="X"/><lb n="0051a11" ed="R129"/><l>海藏月當天，<caesura></caesura>毗舍浮如來。</l></lg>
<lb n="0541c03" ed="X"/><lb n="0051a12" ed="R129"/><lg xml:id="lgX74p0541c0301" type="regular"><l>世界慈悲主，<caesura></caesura>塵沙大法王，<caesura></caesura>所求皆遂願。</l>
<lb n="0541c04" ed="X"/><lb n="0051a13" ed="R129"/><l>慧目鑒凡情，<caesura></caesura>揭句忖如來。</l></lg>
<lb n="0541c05" ed="X"/><lb n="0051a14" ed="R129"/><lg xml:id="lgX74p0541c0501" type="regular"><l>身色如金山，<caesura></caesura>端嚴甚微妙，<caesura></caesura>如淨琉璃中，</l>
<lb n="0541c06" ed="X"/><lb n="0051a15" ed="R129"/><l>內現真金像，<caesura></caesura>揭諾迦牟尼。</l></lg>
<lb n="0541c07" ed="X"/><lb n="0051a16" ed="R129"/><lg xml:id="lgX74p0541c0701" type="regular"><l>容顏甚奇妙，<caesura></caesura>光明照十方。<caesura></caesura>我適曾供養，</l>
<lb n="0541c08" ed="X"/><lb n="0051a17" ed="R129"/><l>今復還親覲，<caesura></caesura>迦攝波如來。</l></lg>
<lb n="0541c09" ed="X"/><lb n="0051a18" ed="R129"/><lg xml:id="lgX74p0541c0901" type="regular"><l>聖主天中王，<caesura></caesura>迦陵頻伽聲，<caesura></caesura>哀愍眾生者，</l>
<lb n="0541c10" ed="X"/><lb n="0051b01" ed="R129"/><l>我等今敬禮，<caesura></caesura>我釋迦如來。</l></lg>
<lb n="0541c11" ed="X"/><lb n="0051b02" ed="R129"/><lg xml:id="lgX74p0541c1101" type="regular"><l>願以此功德，<caesura></caesura>普及於一切。<caesura></caesura>我等與眾生，</l>
<lb n="0541c12" ed="X"/><lb n="0051b03" ed="R129"/><l>皆共成佛道。</l></lg>
<lb n="0541c13" ed="X"/><lb n="0051b04" ed="R129"/><list rend="no-marker"><item xml:id="itemX74p0541c1301">七佛□河王</item><item xml:id="itemX74p0541c1306">浪淘沙</item><item xml:id="itemX74p0541c1309"><g ref="#CB17024"/>伽河王</item><item xml:id="itemX74p0541c1313">信度河王</item>
<lb n="0541c14" ed="X"/><lb n="0051b05" ed="R129"/><item xml:id="itemX74p0541c1401">嚩芻河王</item><item xml:id="itemX74p0541c1405">嚩芻大河王</item>
<lb n="0541c15" ed="X"/><lb n="0051b06" ed="R129"/><item xml:id="itemX74p0541c1501">枲多河王消灾障</item><item xml:id="itemX74p0541c1508">沒臈婆河王</item>
<lb n="0541c16" ed="X"/><lb n="0051b07" ed="R129"/><item xml:id="itemX74p0541c1601">妙高山王唵嚤吽</item><item xml:id="itemX74p0541c1608">雪山王唵嚤呢吽</item>
<lb n="0541c17" ed="X"/><lb n="0051b08" ed="R129"/><item xml:id="itemX74p0541c1701">香醉山王唵嚤呢叭𡄣吽</item>
<lb n="0541c18" ed="X"/><lb n="0051b09" ed="R129"/><item xml:id="itemX74p0541c1801">百峯山王戶唵嚤呢叭𡄣吽</item></list></cb:div>
<lb n="0541c19" ed="X"/><lb n="0051b10" ed="R129"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu level="1" type="其他">星宿　入清江引</cb:mulu><head>星宿　入清江引</head>
<lb n="0541c20" ed="X"/><lb n="0051b11" ed="R129"/><lg xml:id="lgX74p0541c2001"><l>宿宿有有二十八，<caesura></caesura>南無東方阿閦佛。</l>
<lb n="0541c21" ed="X"/><lb n="0051b12" ed="R129"/><l>南方號寶生，<caesura></caesura>西方無量等，<caesura></caesura>北方成就尊，</l>
<lb n="0541c22" ed="X"/><lb n="0051b13" ed="R129"/><l>南無中方毗盧佛，<caesura></caesura>星宿刧千佛々々々々。</l>
<lb n="0541c23" ed="X"/><lb n="0051b14" ed="R129"/><l>七宿星官垂加護。<caesura></caesura>南無大熾盛光王佛。</l>
<lb n="0541c24" ed="X"/><lb n="0051b15" ed="R129"/><l>仰啟消灾熾盛光，<caesura></caesura>領諸星宿下天堂。</l>
<pb n="0542a" ed="X" xml:id="X74.1479.0542a"/>
<lb n="0542a01" ed="X"/><lb n="0051b16" ed="R129"/><l>二十八宿分左右，<caesura></caesura>十二宮辰列兩行。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb n="0542a02" ed="X"/><lb n="0051b17" ed="R129"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu level="1" type="其他">東門七宿</cb:mulu><head>東門七宿</head>
<lb n="0542a03" ed="X"/><lb n="0051b18" ed="R129"/><lg xml:id="lgX74p0542a0301" type="regular"><l>中天星斗與南辰，<caesura></caesura>列耀森羅及眾真。</l>
<lb n="0542a04" ed="X"/><lb n="0052a01" ed="R129"/><l>能發志心求懺悔，<caesura></caesura>灾殃殄滅福駢臻。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb n="0542a05" ed="X"/><lb n="0052a02" ed="R129"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu level="1" type="其他">南門七宿</cb:mulu><head>南門七宿</head>
<lb n="0542a06" ed="X"/><lb n="0052a03" ed="R129"/><lg xml:id="lgX74p0542a0601" type="regular"><l>銀河湛湛蟾光照，<caesura></caesura>慧日騰騰燦太虗。</l>
<lb n="0542a07" ed="X"/><lb n="0052a04" ed="R129"/><l>福海滔滔如淵濟，<caesura></caesura>壽山隱隱等須彌。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb n="0542a08" ed="X"/><lb n="0052a05" ed="R129"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu level="1" type="其他">西門七宿</cb:mulu><head>西門七宿</head>
<lb n="0542a09" ed="X"/><lb n="0052a06" ed="R129"/><lg xml:id="lgX74p0542a0901" type="regular"><l>太陽星斗太阥真，<caesura></caesura>金木水火土德君。</l>
<lb n="0542a10" ed="X"/><lb n="0052a07" ed="R129"/><l>紫炁羅睺并月孛，<caesura></caesura>流年運限及生辰。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb n="0542a11" ed="X"/><lb n="0052a08" ed="R129"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu level="1" type="其他">北門七宿</cb:mulu><head>北門七宿</head>
<lb n="0542a12" ed="X"/><lb n="0052a09" ed="R129"/><lg xml:id="lgX74p0542a1201" type="regular"><l>角亢底房心尾箕，<caesura></caesura>斗牛女虗危室壁。</l>
<lb n="0542a13" ed="X"/><lb n="0052a10" ed="R129"/><l>奎婁胃昴畢觜參，<caesura></caesura>井鬼柳星張翼軫。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb n="0542a14" ed="X"/><lb n="0052a11" ed="R129"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu level="1" type="其他">二十八宿</cb:mulu><head>二十八宿</head>
<lb n="0542a15" ed="X"/><lb n="0052a12" ed="R129"/><lg xml:id="lgX74p0542a1501" type="regular"><l>阿難陀佛妙難量，<caesura></caesura>三卷真詮廣敷揚。</l>
<lb n="0542a16" ed="X"/><lb n="0052a13" ed="R129"/><l>二十八宿添壽筭，<caesura></caesura>十二宮辰保安康。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb n="0542a17" ed="X"/><lb n="0052a14" ed="R129"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu level="1" type="其他">九曜官星</cb:mulu><head>九曜官星</head>
<lb n="0542a18" ed="X"/><lb n="0052a15" ed="R129"/><lg xml:id="lgX74p0542a1801" type="regular"><l>萬像森羅除灾障，<caesura></caesura>滿天星斗降禎祥。</l>
<lb n="0542a19" ed="X"/><lb n="0052a16" ed="R129"/><l>檀信演經從此去，<caesura></caesura>壽山高聳福綿長。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb n="0542a20" ed="X"/><lb n="0052a17" ed="R129"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu level="1" type="其他">滿天星斗一句神仙侶</cb:mulu><head>滿天星斗</head>
<lb n="0542a21" ed="X"/><lb n="0052a18" ed="R129"/><lg xml:id="lgX74p0542a2101" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:0em;" type="regular"><l style="text-indent:1em">一句神仙侶，<caesura style="text-indent:1em;"></caesura>二句五通神仙侶。<caesura style="text-indent:1em;"></caesura>三句五通得道
<lb n="0542a22" ed="X"/><lb n="0052b01" ed="R129"/>神仙侶。</l><l style="text-indent:1em">四句大五通得道神仙侶。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb n="0542a23" ed="X"/><lb n="0052b02" ed="R129"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu level="1" type="其他">到毒藥一句毒藥</cb:mulu><head>到毒藥</head>
<lb n="0542a24" ed="X"/><lb n="0052b03" ed="R129"/><lg xml:id="lgX74p0542a2401" style="margin-left:0em;text-indent:0em;"><l style="text-indent:1em">一句毒藥，<caesura style="text-indent:1em;"></caesura>二句毒藥神，<caesura style="text-indent:1em;"></caesura>三句大毒藥，<caesura style="text-indent:1em;"></caesura>四句藥
<pb n="0542b" ed="X" xml:id="X74.1479.0542b"/>
<lb n="0542b01" ed="X"/><lb n="0052b04" ed="R129"/>王藥上二菩薩。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb n="0542b02" ed="X"/><lb n="0052b05" ed="R129"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu level="1" type="其他">三寶　入清江引</cb:mulu><head>三寶　入清江引</head>
<lb n="0542b03" ed="X"/><lb n="0052b06" ed="R129"/><lg xml:id="lgX74p0542b0301" type="regular"><l>稽首歸依佛，<caesura></caesura>天宮坐寶臺。<caesura></caesura>有情思渴仰。</l>
<lb n="0542b04" ed="X"/><lb n="0052b07" ed="R129"/><l>早願下生來。<caesura></caesura>歸命禮真如沒䭾耶。</l></lg>
<lb n="0542b05" ed="X"/><lb n="0052b08" ed="R129"/><lg xml:id="lgX74p0542b0501" type="regular"><l>稽首歸依法，<caesura></caesura>三明共六通。<caesura></caesura>河沙經藏開。</l>
<lb n="0542b06" ed="X"/><lb n="0052b09" ed="R129"/><l>總持心印順，<caesura></caesura>無去無亦來。<caesura></caesura>海藏。</l></lg>
<lb n="0542b07" ed="X"/><lb n="0052b10" ed="R129"/><lg xml:id="lgX74p0542b0701" type="regular"><l>稽首歸依僧。<caesura></caesura>三明共六通。<caesura></caesura>靈山親授記。</l>
<lb n="0542b08" ed="X"/><lb n="0052b11" ed="R129"/><l>三會願相逢。<caesura></caesura>福田。</l></lg>
<lb n="0542b09" ed="X"/><lb n="0052b12" ed="R129"/><lg xml:id="lgX74p0542b0901" type="regular"><l>稽首僧三寶，<caesura></caesura>眾生良福田。<caesura></caesura>若能歸向者，</l>
<lb n="0542b10" ed="X"/><lb n="0052b13" ed="R129"/><l>獲福廣無邊，<caesura></caesura>佛法僧三寶。</l></lg>
<lb n="0542b11" ed="X"/><lb n="0052b14" ed="R129"/><lg xml:id="lgX74p0542b1101" type="regular"><l>摩訶摩瑜利，<caesura></caesura>佛母明王經。<caesura></caesura>我今歸命禮。</l>
<lb n="0542b12" ed="X"/><lb n="0052b15" ed="R129"/><l>罪滅福源增，<caesura></caesura>摩訶摩瑜利。</l></lg>
<lb n="0542b13" ed="X"/><lb n="0052b16" ed="R129"/><lg xml:id="lgX74p0542b1301"><l>天、阿蘇囉、藥叉等<note place="inline">唵吽</note>，<caesura></caesura>來吽法者<note place="inline">唵吽</note>應志心。</l>
<lb n="0542b14" ed="X"/><lb n="0052b17" ed="R129"/><l>吽唵嚤呢吽。<caesura></caesura>一報天地，<caesura></caesura>二報日月。</l>
<lb n="0542b15" ed="X"/><lb n="0052b18" ed="R129"/><l>三報國王，<caesura></caesura>四報爺娘，<caesura></caesura>願消三障。</l>
<lb n="0542b16" ed="X"/><lb n="0053a01" ed="R129"/><l>以上因緣，<caesura></caesura>摩訶般若。</l></lg>
<lb n="0542b17" ed="X"/><lb n="0053a02" ed="R129"/><p xml:id="pX74p0542b1701">孔<g ref="#CB15179"/>明王佛。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0542b18" ed="X"/><lb n="0053a03" ed="R129"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu level="1" type="其他">三卷圓滿保平安</cb:mulu><head>三卷圓滿保平安</head>
<lb n="0542b19" ed="X"/><lb n="0053a04" ed="R129"/><p xml:id="pX74p0542b1901">南無大孔<g ref="#CB15179"/>明王佛。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0542b20" ed="X"/><lb n="0053a06" ed="R129"/><cb:div type="w"><p xml:id="pX74p0542b2001" style="margin-left:1em"><note n="0542b2001" resp="CBETA" type="add" note_key="X74.0542b20.01">浙【CB】，淅【卍續】</note><app n="0542b2001"><lem resp="CBETA.ting" wit="【CB】">浙</lem><rdg wit="【卍續】">淅</rdg></app>江嘉興府桐鄉縣僧會司下青鎮寶閣禪寺稟
<lb n="0542b21" ed="X"/><lb n="0053a07" ed="R129"/>佛報恩沙門　慧日，　捐貲請續抄寫
<lb n="0542b22" ed="X" type="honorific"/><lb n="0053a08" ed="R129"/>孔<g ref="#CB15179"/>尊經六部，　功德工荐。　考姜公　玭王氏，
<lb n="0542b23" ed="X"/><lb n="0053a09" ed="R129"/>仗此經功，早生工品者。</p>
<lb n="0542b24" ed="X"/><lb n="0053a10" ed="R129"/><p xml:id="pX74p0542b2401">嘉靖三十年季月　日抄白。</p></cb:div>
</body></text></TEI>